    {
      "id": "E:note:row417636:1",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "This is a 66 yr old female (Indian speaking), who was admitted via the    ED fro",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row417636#s1",
      "text": "This is a 66 yr old female (Indian speaking), who was admitted via the    ED from an OSH (on [**Location (un) 1479**]), where she presented w/ c/o difficulty    breathing and chest pain for a couple of days."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row417636:2",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "She was dx ed with    cardiomyopathy at the OSH.",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row417636#s2",
      "text": "She was dx ed with    cardiomyopathy at the OSH."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row417636:3",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Here, her CXR was notable for bilateral    pleural effusions with e/o pulmonary ",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row417636#s3",
      "text": "Here, her CXR was notable for bilateral    pleural effusions with e/o pulmonary edema, and pneumonia could not be    excluded."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row417636:4",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "While in the ED, she was noted to have a BP of 78/38 with a    HR of 76; she was",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row417636#s4",
      "text": "While in the ED, she was noted to have a BP of 78/38 with a    HR of 76; she was given 2L IVF with improvement in BP."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row417636:5",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "She was also    noted to have worsening mental status and became more lethargic ",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row417636#s5",
      "text": "She was also    noted to have worsening mental status and became more lethargic with    this drop in blood pressure."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row417636:6",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "She was tx ed to MICU 6 for further care.",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row417636#s6",
      "text": "She was tx ed to MICU 6 for further care."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row417636:7",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "While in the MICU, she has remained lethargic.",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row417636#s7",
      "text": "While in the MICU, she has remained lethargic."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row417636:8",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "In addition, her HCT has    dropped (requiring tx of 1 unit PRBC) and her ARF ha",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row417636#s8",
      "text": "In addition, her HCT has    dropped (requiring tx of 1 unit PRBC) and her ARF has worsened."
    },
    {
